Installation instructions
=========================
This project uses Puppet for installing software dependencies.
Puppet installation instructions are available here:

http://docs.puppetlabs.com/guides/installation.html

Make sure to install the "rcoleman/puppet_module" puppet module, e.g. like this:

> sudo puppet module install rcoleman/puppet_module

On Windows hosts, make sure that you run all puppet commands with admin privileges, as described here:

http://docs.puppetlabs.com/windows/running.html

Development machine
====================

Preparation of development machine
-----------------------------------
> sudo puppet apply install/dev.pp

Compile static stuff and prepare SQLite database
------------------------------------------------
> ./setup.py build
> ./manage.py syncdb
> ./manage.py migrate

Run development server
----------------------
> ./manage.py runserver

Compile install packages to ./dist on developer machine
-------------------------------------------------------
> ./setup.py build sdist

Production machine
==================

Installation of production backend server
-----------------------------------------
> sudo puppet apply install/prod_backend.pp

Install new release on production web server
--------------------------------------------
> sudo puppet apply install/prod_web.pp

